content.p: Welcome information Missed an email? You'll find a copy here We will send you regular email updates throughout the Welcome period to help you navigate any tasks you need to complete as a new student at Nottingham. If you think you’ve missed an email, you’ll find a copy on this page. Please note that not all communications will be featured on this page. Some course-specific communications may be missing, as well as those relating to any particular circumstance that falls outside of the typical student experience.
